      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1rem;">Entrepreneur · Builder · Writer</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Hi — I'm Albert. I build companies at the intersection of technology and real-world problems.
        Currently co-founding <a href="https://genlayer.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GenLayer</a>,
        an AI-native blockchain, and <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rally</a> [TODO: add link].
      </p>

      <p>
        I live in Spain with my wife and four kids, which has taught me more about prioritization
        and context-switching than any productivity book ever could.
      </p>

      <p>
        This blog is where I think out loud — about startups, technology, strategy, and occasionally
        the chaos of building things while raising a family. I try to write the posts I wish I
        had found when I was starting out.
      </p>

